  "essay_preview": "GED and learned English after coming to the United States legally. Even though I knew this \nthroughout my life, it never held me back from trying my hardest, as he always told me to do.\nHe truly came from nothing, but still gave me everything. While growing up, my father worked as a \nlong-distance truck driver, also known as an OTR. He traveled all across the country from the border \nof Canada to the state of Arizona, and even when he was out for weeks at a time, he would never \nforget about me."
